<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .rejection-reason {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #f5576c;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        h3 {
            color: #f5576c;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #667eea;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        li {
            padding: 8px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Application Update</h1>
            <p>Your tutor profile application status</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= userName %>,</h2>
            
            <p>Thank you for your interest in becoming a tutor on SkillBridge. We appreciate the effort you put into your application.</p>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>📌 Application Status:</strong> <span style="color: #f5576c; font-weight: bold;">Not Approved</span>
            </div>

            <h3>Reason for the Decision:</h3>
            <div class="rejection-reason">
                <%= rejectionReason %>
            </div>

            <h3>What Can You Do Next?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Review the feedback provided above</li>
                <li>Address the mentioned points in your profile</li>
                <li>Resubmit your application after improvements</li>
                <li>Contact our support team for more specific guidance</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>📞 We're Here to Help</h3>
            <p>If you'd like more detailed feedback on your application or have questions about the requirements, feel free to reach out to our team:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> support@skillbridge.com</li>
                <li><strong>Response Time:</strong> Usually within 24 hours</li>
            </ul>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">We encourage you to reapply when you think your profile meets all our requirements. We look forward to seeing you as a SkillBridge tutor soon!</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br/><strong>Team SkillBridge</strong></p>

            <div class="footer">
                <p>© 2026 SkillBridge. All rights reserved.<br/>
                This is an automated message, please do not reply directly.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
